audits/2026-07-11-v1.14-design/E4-empirical-anchors.md:71:## 6. Honest limits
audits/2026-07-11-v1.14-design/E4-empirical-anchors.md:72:- All magnitudes are **political-opinion** perception; **transport to public-project value is an assumption**, to
audits/2026-07-11-v1.14-design/E4-empirical-anchors.md:73:  be flagged, not asserted.
audits/2026-07-11-v1.14-design/E4-empirical-anchors.md:74:- These anchor the **mechanism, structural form, and plausible ranges** — they do **not** yield a real-world
audits/2026-07-11-v1.14-design/E4-empirical-anchors.md:75:  multiplier, and E4 stays a parity-surface/sensitivity result, reported conditionally.
audits/2026-07-11-v1.14-design/E4-empirical-anchors.md:76:- Next: full reads of the three papers for exact coefficients + confirm with Codex's scan when its limit resets.
audits/2026-07-11-v1.14-design/E4-empirical-anchors.md:78:## Sources
