audits/2026-07-11-v1.14-design/E4-empirical-anchors.md:81:- Dias, N. et al. (2025). [drawing the distribution reduces perceived polarization].
audits/2026-07-11-v1.14-design/E4-empirical-anchors.md:82:- Gagnon-Bartsch, T. et al. "Failures in Forecasting: An Experiment on Interpersonal Projection Bias."
