136:5. **MAJOR — the retired statement survives in an active foundation document.** `research/e4-value-estimation-foundation.md:58-63` still says the new surface “extends” `beta=1-eta`, while v3 says it is retired. Amend that note to point to the separate legacy nested-harm theorem. Keeping both claims invites conceptual relapse even if the v3 engine is isolated.
